Ascom Seeks Buyers for Security Business, SonntagsZeitung Says

-- B y   T h o m a s   M u l i e r
-- 
2011-07-17T10:56:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/ascom-seeks-buyers-for-security-business-sonntagszeitung-says.html
Ascom Holding AG, a Swiss
communications company, is seeking buyers for its communication
security assets, SonntagsZeitung said, without saying how it got
the information.  Ascom might sell the business in separate parts, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Mulier in Geneva at 
 tmulier@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Risser at   drisser@bloomberg.net . 